snippet.title: Slime Song: Slime Rancher Remixed
snippet.description:
Remix master Chetreo made this song entirely out of sound effects from Monomi Park's wiggly adventure, Slime Rancher. The game is now available at retail for Xbox One and PS4!

Buy now: https://www.skybound.com/slime-rancher/

#SlimeSong

Remix by: Chetreo
youtube.com/chetreo
Twitter: @Chetreo
Facebook: facebook.com/chetreo

Developed by Monomi Park
www.slimerancher.com
www.monomipark.com
Follow us on Twitter: @monomipark

Retail release published by Skybound Games
www.skyboundgames.com
